e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:44:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>高登=魏，LIHKG=蜀，膠登=吳<br />\n<br />\n三國鼎立，邪不能勝正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n魏會滅蜀喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾正確<br />\n魏仲人多勢眾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n膠登先係蜀 繼魏後首先稱帝 又早衰落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吳國係lihkg 暫時據長江之險同魏分庭抗禮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為鐘意蜀所以先LIHKG=蜀😚<br />\n<br />\n而且蜀國人雖少但係全部都係精英，好似LIHKG咁人少但全部係active user<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但蜀國好多精英都死得早 吳國代代都督都能領導眾將抵禦外敵<br />\nBtw 膠登而家似乎都有點中興<br />\n早排上去好似死氣沉沉 第一頁頁底已經係個幾鐘<br />\n而家第一頁頁底都有半個鐘"},{"pid":"5f9a67e707664340e33a211fb1cb12c37964d64c","tid":8012,"uid":11950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T18:45:44.000Z","msg":"魏係邪係咪三國演義上腦"},{"pid":"6e8f2503a3d105f3fa670b35529b49a2e0ffb274","tid":8012,"uid":2295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T19:02:58.000Z","msg":"咁講最尾咪三國歸晉<br />\n邊個係司馬家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5c9919a99b9d6bc9303494f1aad9ec0da2eb6d","tid":8012,"uid":2295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T19:06:09.000Z","msg":"我理解係<br />\n高登=魏 hkg+=蜀 膠登=吳<br />\nLihkg=晉<br />\n<br />\n至於三國最後既大贏家<br />\n司馬懿唔洗諗都知係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}